### ─── Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Login (admin del seed)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

###

### Perfil propio
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Books ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar libros
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books

###

### Buscar por título, autor o género
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books?search=quijote

###

### Filtrar por género
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books?genre=Novela&available=true

###

### Paginación
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books?page=1&limit=5

###

### Obtener libro por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/1

###

### Crear libro (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "El Principito",
  "author": "Antoine de Saint-Exupéry",
  "genre": "Fábula",
  "isbn": "978-84-261-3229-7",
  "synopsis": "Un piloto conoce a un pequeño príncipe venido de otro planeta.",
  "year": 1943,
  "totalCopies": 5
}

###

### Actualizar libro (admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/books/5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "totalCopies": 10,
  "available": true
}

###

### Eliminar libro (admin)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/books/5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Loans ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Solicitar préstamo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookId": 1,
  "dueDate": "2026-04-30T23:59:59.000Z"
}

###

### Mis préstamos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/loans/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Todos los préstamos (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Filtrar préstamos activos (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/loans?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Devolver libro
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Reviews ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Ver reseñas de un libro
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews

###

### Crear reseña
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Una obra maestra de la literatura universal."
}

###

### Actualizar reseña
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Muy buena, aunque un poco extensa."
}

###

### Eliminar reseña
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

